<note n="0063001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063001">本文 saṅkâbhisekavassena 是 sakâbhisekavassena？</note>
<note n="0063002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063002">本文 nattā te ahesuṁ 是 nattāro ahesuṁ？</note>
<note n="0063003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063003">本文 Rohinī 是 Rohana。</note>
<note n="0064004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064004">Dovārikamaṇḍala 成為大王統史之 Dvāramaṇḍlaka 依據大王統史二十三．二三於阿<g ref="#CB00145">㝹</g>羅陀市之東支提附近之村。</note>
</p>
